## ğŸš€ Getting Started

1. **Install Dependencies**

npm install @apollo/server graphql

2. **Start the Server**

node index.js

3. **Access GraphQL Playground**
   Navigate to `http://localhost:4000`

## ğŸ“ Example Queries

### Fetch All Users

query {
getUsers {
id
name
email
isAdmin
}
}

### Create User

mutation {
createUser(
name: "John Doe"
email: "john@example.com"
isAdmin: true
) {
id
name
email
}
}

